Short description:
Lightweight earbuds built for gaming.
HyperX Cloud MIX Buds are true wireless earbuds designed for gaming and feature a low-latency 2.4GHz connection. Light and comfortable, the dual wireless Cloud MIX Buds have a USB Type-C wireless adapter for ultra-low latency gaming, and a convenient Bluetooth&reg; connection for listening to music or answering phone calls when you&rsquo;re on the go. The included USB-C to USB-C passthrough extender lets you bring the adapter closer to you for improved wireless performance during desktop PC gaming. When connected to PC, players can take advantage of DTS Headphone:X&reg;, which ups immersion by providing virtual 3D spatial audio with precise sound localization. Three included ear tip sizes ensure that you&rsquo;ll have a secure, personalized fit with signature HyperX comfort. With up to 33 hours of battery life on a single charge, you&rsquo;ll have plenty of juice to keep the good times going.	- Dual Wireless TWS: 2.4GHz | Bluetooth&reg;
	- Signature HyperX comfort and durability
	- HyperX Signature sound + DTS Headphone:X&reg;
