Short description:
Your business projector for office and home office.
With the Acer P5535 you get the usual quality and performance you know from the predecessor P5530. The only difference: more brightness.
Thanks to 4,500 ANSI lumens, the P5535 is even brighter and enables daytime projection even in stronger light. Even in Eco mode, the P5535 achieves around 3,600 ANSI lumens. A strong contrast of 20,000:1 and powerful 16W speakers round out the powerhouse.	- Light technology: 240 watt Philips UHP
